### Get current user
GET http://localhost:8080/auth/me

### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":"email1",
  "password":"password1"
}

### Login user
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email":"email1",
  "password":"password1"
}

### Logout user
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
